"\n"
"\n"
"Orcs who were not the strongest of their litter tend to specialize in other "
"skills, like archery or assassination."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"同族の強者には及ばないオークは、弓術や暗殺といった他のスキルを磨きます。"

